criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age > 18 years old

          -  acquisition of informed consent for surgery and for inclusion in the study;

          -  elective open or laparoscopic PD

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  age <to 18 years;

          -  absence of informed consent for inclusion in the study;

          -  Emergency surgery;

          -  other pancreatic resections (not PD).
